## ApiSources-A2 APIs Documentation View Architecture
**Status:** approved
**Tags:** stack:frontend

- Static documentation living in `specs/apis.ad`; rendered as a read-only view in the frontend
- Grouped by backend module: Forge, Relay, Config, Wiki, Raw
- Each entry shows HTTP method, route path, handler function, and one-line description
- Editable through the Specs workspace when `apis.ad` is updated
